 zašto si ljut?

1179
00:45:21,680 --> 00:45:23,780
 Zašto ti je lice namrgođeno?

1180
00:45:23,780 --> 00:45:26,040
 Jer ako pravo radiš,

1181
00:45:26,040 --> 00:45:27,060
 vedrinom ocijevaš.

1182
00:45:27,060 --> 00:45:28,140
 A ne radiš li pravo,

1183
00:45:28,140 --> 00:45:29,640
 grijeh ti je kao zvijer na pragu

1184
00:45:29,640 --> 00:45:30,820
 što na te vreba

1185
00:45:30,820 --> 00:45:31,900
 i još mu se možeš

1186
00:45:31,900 --> 00:45:32,980
 oduprijed.

1187
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:35,660
 Da nije super da mu se

1188
00:45:35,660 --> 00:45:36,520
 Bog obratio

1189
00:45:36,520 --> 00:45:37,740
 ko neki učitelj,

1190
00:45:37,740 --> 00:45:38,500
 ko neki mentor.

1191
00:45:38,500 --> 00:45:39,660
 Pita ga

1192
00:45:39,660 --> 00:45:40,560
 zašto si ljut?

1193
00:45:40,560 --> 00:45:42,580
 Ej,

1194
00:45:42,580 --> 00:45:43,680
 nemoj vjerovat

1195
00:45:43,680 --> 00:45:44,460
 tim mislima

1196
00:45:44,460 --> 00:45:45,480
 koje ti se vrte u glavi.

1197
00:45:45,480 --> 00:45:46,940
 Nemoj vjerovat

1198
00:45:46,940 --> 00:45:47,380
 tim mislima

1199
00:45:47,380 --> 00:45:48,140
 koje ti se vrte u glavi.

1200
00:45:48,140 --> 00:45:50,480
 Možeš vladat na njima,

1201
00:45:50,480 --> 00:45:51,700
 možeš ih pobjedit.

1202
00:45:51,700 --> 00:45:53,720
 Nemoj vjerovat.

1203
00:45:53,720 --> 00:45:55,040
 Bojstvo se dogodilo kasnije.

1204
00:45:55,400 --> 00:45:56,140
 Ovo je trenutak

1205
00:45:56,140 --> 00:45:57,340
 kada ga Bog diže.

1206
00:45:57,340 --> 00:45:59,120
 Bog vidi šta mu se događa.

1207
00:45:59,120 --> 00:46:00,620
 Bog vidi šta može biti

1208
00:46:00,620 --> 00:46:01,120
 u tom srcu

1209
00:46:01,120 --> 00:46:02,360
 ako on pristane na te misli,

1210
00:46:02,360 --> 00:46:03,760
 ako on pristane na te osjećaje.

1211
00:46:03,760 --> 00:46:05,160
 I Bog mu doslovno dolazi.

1212
00:46:05,160 --> 00:46:06,780
 Ono, znam da ti je sad teško.

1213
00:46:06,780 --> 00:46:07,820
 Dolazi je meni.

1214
00:46:07,820 --> 00:46:08,880
 E, znam da ti je sad teško.

1215
00:46:08,880 --> 00:46:09,620
 Znam da prolaziš

1216
00:46:09,620 --> 00:46:10,540
 teške stvari na poslu.

1217
00:46:10,540 --> 00:46:11,880
 Znam da si umoran od svega.

1218
00:46:11,880 --> 00:46:12,540
 Znam da čekaš

1219
00:46:12,540 --> 00:46:13,380
 već dugo rješenje.

1220
00:46:13,380 --> 00:46:15,240
 Znam kroz šta prolaziš.

1221
00:46:15,240 --> 00:46:15,560
 Ej,

1222
00:46:15,560 --> 00:46:17,340
 ali nemoj pristati

1223
00:46:17,340 --> 00:46:17,860
 na sve misli

1224
00:46:17,860 --> 00:46:18,580
 koji ti dolaze.

1225
00:46:18,580 --> 00:46:21,900
 Ja imam dovoljno.

1226
00:46:21,900 --> 00:46:24,400
 Tako se obraća.

1227
00:46:24,400 --> 00:46:27,020
 Nije mu rekao

1228
00:46:27,020 --> 00:46:28,340
 daj, molim te, šta je glumiš?

1229
00:46:28,340 --> 00:46:30,400
 Šta plaćiš?

1230
00:46:30,400 --> 00:46:31,620
 Šta plaćiš?

1231
00:46:31,620 --> 00:46:32,220
 Abel je,

1232
00:46:32,220 --> 00:46:33,600
 njegovu žrtvu sam pogledao,

1233
00:46:33,600 --> 00:46:34,300
 tvoju nisam.

1234
00:46:34,300 --> 00:46:34,980
 Daj, molim te.

1235
00:46:34,980 --> 00:46:37,400
 Tako mi razgovaramo.

1236
00:46:37,400 --> 00:46:38,400
 Ma daj, šta je plaći?

1237
00:46:38,400 --> 00:46:39,600
 Ma šta je glumi?

1238
00:46:39,600 --> 00:46:40,720
 Ma nijemo ništa.

1239
00:46:40,720 --> 00:46:42,000
 Ma daj, molim te.

1240
00:46:42,000 --> 00:46:43,020
 Ma ajde.

1241
00:46:43,020 --> 00:46:44,180
 Biće dobro.

1242
00:46:47,700 --> 00:46:48,800
 Bog tako ne razgovara.

1243
00:46:48,800 --> 00:46:50,720
 To mi tako razgovaramo.

1244
00:46:50,720 --> 00:46:52,100
 Ali Bog tako ne razgovara.

1245
00:46:52,100 --> 00:46:54,980
 I bi mi svi voljeli

1246
00:46:54,980 --> 00:46:55,820
 ovakav razgovor.

1247
00:46:55,820 --> 00:46:57,400
 Kad smo mi dolje,

1248
00:46:57,400 --> 00:46:58,020
 kad smo mi

1249
00:46:58,020 --> 00:46:59,420
 u zabrinutosti,

1250
00:46:59,420 --> 00:47:00,260
 mi bi htjeli ovo.

1251
00:47:00,260 --> 00:47:01,000
 Isi dobro?

1252
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:03,200
 Još mu objašnjava.

1253
00:47:03,200 --> 00:47:04,720
 Zašto si ljut?

1254
00:47:04,720 --> 00:47:06,460
 Ono, kužim te.

1255
00:47:06,460 --> 00:47:08,160
 Okej da si sad ljut.

1256
00:47:08,160 --> 00:47:09,380
 Okej da si sad frustriran.

1257
00:47:09,380 --> 00:47:10,440
 Ej, ali nemoj pristati

1258
00:47:10,440 --> 00:47:10,940
 na sve misli

1259
00:47:10,940 --> 00:47:11,740
 koje ti sad dolaze.

1260
00:47:11,740 --> 00:47:13,580
 Nemoj ostati u tome.

1261
00:47:13,580 --> 00:47:15,760
 Bog ima dovoljno.

1262
00:47:17,540 --> 00:47:20,220
 to je doslovno

1263
00:47:20,220 --> 00:47:21,060
 kao djete

1264
00:47:21,060 --> 00:47:21,760
 kad učiš ono.

1265
00:47:21,760 --> 00:47:22,520
 Jošua,

1266
00:47:22,520 --> 00:47:24,460
 kad je bio,

1267
00:47:24,460 --> 00:47:25,140
 morali smo ga

1268
00:47:25,140 --> 00:47:26,120
 ono, ispitivati kao

1269
00:47:26,120 --> 00:47:26,640
 jesi ljut?

1270
00:47:26,640 --> 00:47:27,960
 Jesi tužan?

1271
00:47:27,960 --> 00:47:28,920
 Jesi,

1272
00:47:28,920 --> 00:47:30,380
 ne znam,

1273
00:47:30,380 --> 00:47:31,220
 razočaran sad?

1274
00:47:31,220 --> 00:47:31,760
 Jesi li,

1275
00:47:31,760 --> 00:47:33,240
 ne znam,

1276
00:47:33,240 --> 00:47:34,100
 jel te boli nešto?

1277
00:47:34,100 --> 00:47:34,940
 Ono,

1278
00:47:34,940 --> 00:47:35,760
 pitati ga točno.

1279
00:47:35,760 --> 00:47:36,960
 I on je točno znao reći,

1280
00:47:36,960 --> 00:47:37,480
 ne ljut sam,

1281
00:47:37,480 --> 00:47:38,280
 ne tužan sam,

1282
00:47:38,280 --> 00:47:40,040
 razlikovao emocije.

1283
00:47:40,040 --> 00:47:43,380
 Jesi zabrinut?

1284
00:47:44,580 --> 00:47:45,700
 Točno je razlikovao.

1285
00:47:45,700 --> 00:47:47,960
 Moro sam ga naučiti.

1286
00:47:47,960 --> 00:47:49,280
 Bog isto radi s nama.

1287
00:47:49,280 --> 00:47:50,420
 Ej, šta ti sad?

1288
00:47:50,420 --> 00:47:52,860
 Ej, Kajne,

1289
00:47:52,860 --> 00:47:54,100
 šta je bilo?

1290
00:47:54,100 --> 00:47:55,220
 Zašto ti je lice namrgođeno?

1291
00:47:55,220 --> 00:47:56,800
 Ako si sve dobro napravio,

1292
00:47:56,800 --> 00:47:57,680
 zašto si namršten?

1293
00:47:57,680 --> 00:48:00,780
 Zašto si ljut?

1294
00:48:00,940 --> 00:48:01,300
 Marta,

1295
00:48:01,300 --> 00:48:02,320
 zašto si ljuta na Mariju?

1296
00:48:02,320 --> 00:48:03,360
 Ako ti sve dobro radiš,

1297
00:48:03,360 --> 00:48:05,460
 ako ti Marta radiš ono što ti je Bog rekao da radiš,

1298
00:48:05,460 --> 00:48:07,740
 ako si ti sigurna da trebaš okolo sad trčati i poslužiti,

1299
00:48:07,740 --> 00:48:09,860
 pa šta si ti ljuta zato što Marija sjedi?

1300
00:48:09,860 --> 00:48:11,960
 E,

1301
00:48:11,960 --> 00:48:13,700
 ali ja se trudim,

1302
00:48:13,700 --> 00:48:14,520
 ja radim,

1303
00:48:14,520 --> 00:48:15,560
 a oni samo sjede,

1304
00:48:15,560 --> 00:48:17,000
 oni samo nisu sve napravili,

1305
00:48:17,000 --> 00:48:18,120
 o, niko ništa,

1306
00:48:18,120 --> 00:48:19,980
 ja sam danas napravio to,

1307
00:48:19,980 --> 00:48:20,640
 ovi nisu.

1308
00:48:20,640 --> 00:48:22,580
 Kao, pa okej,

1309
00:48:22,580 --> 00:48:23,580
 jel trebaš ti to raditi?

1310
00:48:23,580 --> 00:48:24,720
 Da,

1311
00:48:24,720 --> 00:48:25,680
 i si ti to izabrao?

1312
00:48:25,680 --> 00:48:25,860
 Da.

1313
00:48:25,860 --> 00:48:27,000
 Pa ti napravi.

1314
00:48:27,000 --> 00:48:29,760
 Okej.

1315
00:48:30,400 --> 00:48:30,800
 Bog kaže,

1316
00:48:30,800 --> 00:48:32,040
 ja te vidim.

1317
00:48:32,040 --> 00:48:34,600
 Ja te vidim.

1318
00:48:34,600 --> 00:48:39,540
 E, ali ovi se nisu toliko trudili koliko sam se trudio.

1319
00:48:39,540 --> 00:48:40,120
 Pa okej.

1320
00:48:40,120 --> 00:48:42,520
 Jesi ti imao poziv za to?

1321
00:48:42,520 --> 00:48:42,720
 Da.

1322
00:48:42,720 --> 00:48:44,160
 Jesi ti dao sve od sebe?

1323
00:48:44,160 --> 00:48:44,340
 Da.

1324
00:48:44,340 --> 00:48:45,380
 Pa ti se napravi dobro.

1325
00:48:45,380 --> 00:48:45,900
 Like.

1326
00:48:45,900 --> 00:48:48,340
 S njim ću razgovarati poslije,

1327
00:48:48,340 --> 00:48:49,800
 da nije tvoj problem.

1328
00:48:49,800 --> 00:48:52,520
 Ko što je rekao za Ivana?

1329
00:48:52,520 --> 00:48:54,660
 Šta je ti imaš s tima ako ja njega ostavim do kraja?

1330
00:48:54,660 --> 00:48:56,480
 Petre, boli te briga,

1331
00:48:56,480 --> 00:48:57,720
 ja sam onaj koji odlučuje.

1332
00:48:57,720 --> 00:48:59,060
 Ivan će ostati do kraja.

1333
00:48:59,860 --> 00:49:05,020
 jer kaže,

1334
00:49:05,020 --> 00:49:10,620
 grijeh ti kao zvijer na pragu što na te vreba,

1335
00:49:10,620 --> 00:49:12,820
 još mu se možeš oduprijeti.

1336
00:49:15,320 --> 00:49:19,880
 Imamo istu stvar u Novom Zavijetu kad su se apostoli svađali tko od njih najveći.

1337
00:49:19,880 --> 00:49:24,820
 I onda Isus povuči sa strane, ej, tak se svađaju vladari ovoga svijeta.

1338
00:49:24,820 --> 00:49:26,600
 Vi niste takvi.

1339
00:49:26,600 --> 00:49:27,820
 Da nemojte to raditi.

1340
00:49:27,820 --> 00:49:32,460
 Isus priča o Bogu kao otcu koji ima dva sina.

1341
00:49:33,760 --> 00:49:34,920
 starijeg i mlađeg.

1342
00:49:34,920 --> 00:49:36,920
 Mlađi sin koji je prosuo i manje,

1343
00:49:36,920 --> 00:49:40,420
 vratio se nazad i napravimo feštu.

1344
00:49:40,420 --> 00:49:42,640
 Ima starijeg sina koji dolazi iz polja i vi gleda,

1345
00:49:42,640 --> 00:49:47,020
 prosuo je sve i se napravili su feštu, ne mogu vjerovat.

1346
00:49:48,980 --> 00:49:50,940
 I onda dolazi gore i Bog mu ne kaže,

1347
00:49:50,940 --> 00:49:54,400
 a koja ljubom mora nek se odljuti i nek završi s tom pričom,

1348
00:49:54,400 --> 00:49:56,920
 pa nek dođe onda na feštu, može se zabaljati svima ostalima,

1349
00:49:56,920 --> 00:49:58,860
 nek stoje vani dok to ne riješi sam sa sobom.

1350
00:49:58,860 --> 00:50:00,820
 Ne, otac izlazi vani i kaže mu,

1351
00:50:00,820 --> 00:50:05,600
 ej sine, pa moje sve je i tvoje.

1352
00:50:05,600 --> 00:50:07,740
 Ej, ima dovoljno.

1353
00:50:07,740 --> 00:50:12,140
 Njegova poruka za nas je, ej, ima dovoljno.

1354
00:50:12,140 --> 00:50:15,520
 Ima dovoljno.

1355
00:50:18,160 --> 00:50:19,180
 Blago si njima, nama ne.

1356
00:50:19,180 --> 00:50:22,360
 Ne, ima dovoljno.

1357
00:50:22,360 --> 00:50:26,800
 Ima dovoljno, samo dođi.

1358
00:50:26,800 --> 00:50:29,480
 Već je ovo sve bilo tvoje.

1359
00:50:29,480 --> 00:50:31,100
 Treba si im samo pitat.

1360
00:50:31,100 --> 00:50:36,260
 I vidim tvoj bol, vidim tvoju razočaranost,

1361
00:50:36,260 --> 00:50:38,140
 vidim tvoje sad loše osjećaje,

1362
00:50:38,140 --> 00:50:40,200
 vidim sve ono kroz šta prolaziš.

1363
00:50:40,200 --> 00:50:42,760
 Ej, ja ti kažem, ima dovoljno.

1364
00:50:42,760 --> 00:50:47,980
 To je Božja perspektiva.

1365
00:50:47,980 --> 00:50:53,000
 Ljubav ne zavidi.

1366
00:50:53,000 --> 00:50:56,480
 Ljubav ne zavidi.

1367
00:50:56,480 --> 00:51:01,740
 Ako imam problema s tim,

1368
00:51:01,740 --> 00:51:04,220
 onda ću izaći, možda Slavljinički tim se pripremiti.

1369
00:51:04,220 --> 00:51:06,240
 Ako imam problem s nečim,

1370
00:51:06,240 --> 00:51:08,040
 onda ću suprotno toga napraviti.

1371
00:51:08,040 --> 00:51:10,600
 Ako imam problem, strah da ću ostati bez svega,

1372
00:51:10,600 --> 00:51:12,440
 da će biti, daj veliko odrušno.

1373
00:51:15,140 --> 00:51:16,500
 Daj suprotno od toga.

1374
00:51:16,500 --> 00:51:20,060
 Niko me nije pohvalio, nikad mi niko ništa nije lijepo.

1375
00:51:20,060 --> 00:51:22,760
 Ja je rekao, pa izađi van i govori svima ljepi stvari.

1376
00:51:23,300 --> 00:51:24,500
 Recimo ono ljepo što vidiš.

1377
00:51:24,500 --> 00:51:30,020
 Pravi ti suprotno od onoga što misliš da tebi fali.

1378
00:51:32,060 --> 00:51:35,600
 I vidjet ćeš da onda možemo izaći iz ogorčenosti.

1379
00:51:35,600 --> 00:51:39,920
 Isus nam daje upute u govoru na gori.

1380
00:51:39,920 --> 00:51:42,700
 Trebaš dati veliko odrušno, oprostiti veliko odrušno,

1381
00:51:42,700 --> 00:51:46,460
 biti ovdje bez opterećenja, bez opterećivanja,

1382
00:51:46,460 --> 00:51:48,620
 moliti za neprijatelje i častiti druge.

1383
00:51:48,620 --> 00:51:52,820
 Zavidna osoba ne može častiti drugu osobu.

1384
00:51:52,820 --> 00:51:54,760
 Ne mogu častiti nekoga koji je više od mene

1385
00:51:54,760 --> 00:51:57,800
 iskazati mu čast jer sam zavidan.

1386
00:51:57,800 --> 00:52:00,020
 Ja želim odločivati.

1387
00:52:00,020 --> 00:52:01,200
 Je li on neki drugi problem?

1388
00:52:01,200 --> 00:52:04,840
 Ali iskazati čast nekome,

1389
00:52:04,840 --> 00:52:08,140
 bi on na više pozicije od mene ili ne?

1390
00:52:08,140 --> 00:52:13,060
 Dolazi iz ljubavi da to mogu napraviti.

1391
00:52:13,060 --> 00:52:18,060
 Iz zavisti ne mogu onoga nikome pripada dati čast.

1392
00:52:18,060 --> 00:52:23,640
 Jer si mislim, ja nešto zaslužim, ja nešto trebam.

1393
00:52:24,220 --> 00:52:27,880
 Ne, uprvo suprotno, ako želim biti slobodan od toga.

1394
00:52:27,880 --> 00:52:30,620
 Napraviti suprotno.

1395
00:52:30,620 --> 00:52:41,240
 Tako da, zavis nikad ne preste.

1396
00:52:41,240 --> 00:52:43,780
 Kao ni ljubav.

1397
00:52:43,780 --> 00:52:48,400
 Tako da, ako ne želimo biti zavidni,

1398
00:52:48,400 --> 00:52:50,680
 želimo se stvarno iskreno radovati,

1399
00:52:50,680 --> 00:52:51,740
 biti sretni,

1400
00:52:53,560 --> 00:52:55,340
 biti zahvalni za ono gdje se nalazimo.

1401
00:52:55,340 --> 00:52:58,660
 Onda ćemo

1402
00:52:58,660 --> 00:53:00,920
 se boriti s ljubavlji protiv toga.

1403
00:53:00,920 --> 00:53:03,280
 Onda ćemo se dopustiti tamo gdje,

1404
00:53:03,280 --> 00:53:04,820
 kao što je Ciprian rekao,

1405
00:53:04,820 --> 00:53:06,460
 tamo gdje je nastala rana,

1406
00:53:06,460 --> 00:53:08,380
 doći ću tamo i pustit ću si tu tugu.

1407
00:53:08,380 --> 00:53:10,960
 Pustit tu tugu i reći,

1408
00:53:10,960 --> 00:53:13,140
 Bože, želim da ovo bude isciljeno.

1409
00:53:13,140 --> 00:53:15,100
 Sočit ću se s tim.

1410
00:53:15,100 --> 00:53:17,420
 Reći, ovo je stvarno zeznuto.

1411
00:53:17,420 --> 00:53:19,940
 Ovo je stvarno bilo loše.

1412
00:53:19,940 --> 00:53:21,560
 Nije fair.

1413
00:53:21,560 --> 00:53:23,440
 Nije plavilno.

1414
00:53:26,740 --> 00:53:28,440
 Ali ti dajem taj prostor

1415
00:53:28,440 --> 00:53:29,560
 da sada iscijeliš,

1416
00:53:29,560 --> 00:53:32,660
 da budem sada u ovom trenutku sretan,

1417
00:53:32,660 --> 00:53:33,420
 radostan,

1418
00:53:33,420 --> 00:53:35,460
 da mi izvuče svu radost.

1419
00:53:35,460 --> 00:53:39,000
 Taj osjećaj od prije.

1420
00:53:39,000 --> 00:53:41,580
 Bog će to zacijeliti,

1421
00:53:41,580 --> 00:53:42,640
 Bog će izlječiti,

1422
00:53:42,640 --> 00:53:44,760
 i onda ćemo se moći radovati jednim drugima.

1423
00:53:46,900 --> 00:53:47,400
 Amen.

